LaTeX writer: improve rendering of unreferenced footnotes.

The "backrefs" attribute of a `<footnote>` is empty, if there is no matching
`<footnote_reference>` but the `\DUfootnote` command expects a backref.
Use an empty string instead of a self-reference as fallback value.
The LaTeX warning changes from

  name{[...]} has been referenced but does not exist, replaced by a fixed one

to

  Suppressing link with empty target [...]

which is better than a spurious backlink to the document top.
